0000	ADD	Add A and B (with Carry out)                    OK
0001	SUB	Subtract B from A (with Borrow out)             OK
0010	INC	Increment A by 1                                OK
0011	DEC	Decrement A by 1                                OK
0100	AND	Bitwise AND (A & B)                             OK  
0101	OR	Bitwise OR (A | B)                              OK
0110	XOR	Bitwise XOR (A ^ B)                             OK
0111	NOT	Bitwise Invert A (~A)                           OK
1000	SHL_A	Logical Shift Left A (Multiply by 2)        OK
1001	SHR_A	Logical Shift Right A (Divide by 2)         OK
1010	ROL	Rotate Left A (Bit 7 moves to Bit 0)            OK
1011	CMP	Compare A and B (Updates Flags only, OUT = A)   OK
1100	PASS_A	Bypass A directly to output                 OK
1101	CLR	Clear output (OUT = 0)                          OK
1110    HLT. Does absolutely nothing                        OK